      "content": "i guess. but it's more than just being tired. it's like... if the person who made everything make sense is gone, what is the point of any of this? i look at my life and it's just a hollow shell. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will. it doesn't even feel like \"living\" anymore, it just feels like lingering.",
